    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The API parameter [`filters`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/api-parameters/filters/) is what you're looking for.\r\n\r\nThis should work:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nvar search = instantsearch({\r\n  indexName: 'indexname',\r\n  searchClient,\r\n  searchParameters: {\r\n    filters: 'NOT intern:1',\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n```",
